        {
            "id": 6410650,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 恆生科技指數上漲234.38點至4913.48點，漲幅5.01%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間08日01:22，恆生科技指數上漲234.38點（或5.01%），暫報4913.48點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.63%</li><li>近 1 月：-5.42%</li><li>近 3 月：-18.46%</li><li>近 6 月：-28.57%</li><li>今年以來：-15.17%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>銅概念領漲+15.55%。其中    環球戰略集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08007:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08007\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08007-HK</a>)            上漲        49.06%            ;        中國大冶有色金屬(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00661:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00661\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00661-HK</a>)            上漲        13.73%            ;        五礦資源(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01208:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01208\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01208-HK</a>)            上漲        10.3%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>及貴金屬概念領漲+6.86%。其中    大唐<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:08299:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/08299\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">08299-HK</a>)            上漲        11.54%            ;        中國<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02099:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02099\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02099-HK</a>)            上漲        10.88%            ;        潼關<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00340:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00340\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00340-HK</a>)            上漲        10.71%    。</p></section></main>",
